{"data":[{"id":563817788,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a430752c7346e6bd7c3a174ed8c862ca","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":60,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563817788","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546283325,"updated_time":1546284299,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e其实-1是不是质数的绕的那里是有办法强行解释的，关键就看你怎么断句，-1是质数到底是大前提还是条件。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果这样翻译一下：设有集合C，包括所有质数，可能还有一个其他数（接下来讨论的-1）。A则该定义为能表示为两个c中数相加的偶数，那么该同学想要证明的是：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e若-1属于C，则任意偶数属于A\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e逆否命题为存在偶数不属于A，则-1不属于C\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e经过思考，我觉得这个同学想表达的还有可能真的是这个意思（虽然其实只是我的强行解释，但可能性还是存在嘛），只是理解不到位没有说出来\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是很遗憾，就算这个意思也是错的很明显的。因为逆否命题自己是不成立的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-1属不属于C，直接决定于2属不属于A，如果2属于A，那么-1必须属于C，反之亦然。那么问题来了，如果2确实属于A而存在大偶数不属于A呢？-1还是应该属于C，因此，逆否命题并不能确定为真，除非证明上述情况不可能发生，那么，惊不惊喜意不意外，这几乎就等于证哥德巴赫猜想了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得小朋友看不到这个回答，不过我还是准备了一个通俗的例子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果A=1，则A+2=3且今天下雨了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果今天不下雨或A+2≠3，则A≠1\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而小朋友的证明就等于说，因为A+2≠3必有A≠1，所以逆反命题会成立，所以原命题为真所以今天肯定下雨了。错的很明显吧，万一A就是1但是今天没下雨呢？\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"其实-1是不是质数的绕的那里是有办法强行解释的，关键就看你怎么断句，-1是质数到底是大前提还是条件。 如果这样翻译一下：设有集合C，包括所有质数，可能还有一个其他数（接下来讨论的-1）。A则该定义为能表示为两个c中数相加的偶数，那么该同学想要证明的…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=133\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2